snippet.title: Capslock Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
Embark on your creative sandbox journey running a cosy keyboard store! Browse boards, skins, symbols, key caps and more! Sell to your customers, manage your stock & rise to keyboard stardom! 🌟

Wishlist now on Steam! Just search "Capslock" !
